{"tid":1638107,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"越睇越似V煞電影內容","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T07:59:26.000Z","uid":268271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5ffaf89db50faf1000711b162916d964016149fe","tid":1638107,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:04:29.000Z","msg":"其一, 政府自制恐荒, 圖令抗爭者屈服!"},{"pid":"d5f3342293e087437dcc1de27197d2b547519d1b","tid":1638107,"uid":268271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"片中曾提及11月5日是個特別日子"},{"pid":"529459f70b3003fef8fdb8783488b4dc4a8a70d6","tid":1638107,"uid":268271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:12:11.000Z","msg":"片中金句 :<br />\n1. 藝術家籍謊言道出真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n2. 就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿着強大的力量。 （While the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power.）<br />\n<br />\n3. 人民不應該害怕政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。 （People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n4. 力量來自團結，團結來自信念。（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n5. 我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裹，我們是自由的。（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n6. 面具之下不止是肉體，而是理念，肉體可以被子彈殺死，但理念永恆不滅，也無畏無懼。（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof.）<br />\n<br />\n7. 製造恐懼，是政府的終極武器。（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）"},{"pid":"a68d4cec03cd17d38c16e51bc1c2e99b8cf19dea","tid":1638107,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"巧先睇完"},{"pid":"3ed5e0a9f548635c8f6fef3c73ad6426946fc7c5","tid":1638107,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTim